                        <h1><strong>Web Designing Interview Questions</strong></h1>
                        <p>Following are most frequently asked <strong>Web Designing Interview Questions &amp; Answers</strong> for both beginners as well as experienced Web Designers.</p>
                        <p>These common questions are more like a jump start towards your design job, and fully prepare you for your job interview.</p>
                        <p>As companies increasingly rely on attractive web pages to build up their businesses, web designing's importance is constantly increasing. High quality web pages attract people to dig in deep for detailed information and to engage in different activities with the company.</p>
                        <p>These general questions help the hiring team get to know better about you and your interest in the position:</p>
                        <p>What can you tell us about yourself?</p>
